The paper proposes a framework based on reinforcement learning, which is a popular topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also focuses on exploration in control tasks, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of deep learning (cs.DL).
